rows.label: qst500108_msg0001
rows.name: No time for greetings and pleasantries!

rows.label: qst500108_msg0002
rows.name:
Lulili already spend 100 days since
start of searching for tasty-tasty
juice ingredients!

rows.label: qst500108_msg0003
rows.name:
Was walking alongside ruins to find
tasty-tasty Ice Cabbage when slipped
and fell all way down!

rows.label: qst500108_msg0004
rows.name:
Jump down from here too scary,
so Lulili live here for 99 days!

rows.label: qst500108_msg0009
rows.name:
Friends right... Flapping Nopon wings
like bird wings make fall very gentle!

rows.label: qst500108_msg0010
rows.name:
Friends right...maybe less scary to
climb back up than drop further down.

rows.label: qst500108_msg0011
rows.name:
Lulili was caught in trap of thinking that
down is only way to go. That why Lulili
so paralyze by scary-scary.

rows.label: qst500108_msg0012
rows.name:
Why Lulili not see such obvious option?
Brain must be freezed by annoy of not
finding Ice Cabbage. Or cold weather.

rows.label: qst500108_msg0014
rows.name:
Actually, Lulili have other brotherpons
and sisterpons searching for tasty-tasty
juice ingredients too.

rows.label: qst500108_msg0015
rows.name:
Maybe friends meet them somewhere?
Please say hello-lo from Lulili if yes!
